✅ **Legend / Notes:**

- Heroes progress from Beginner → OD over Seasons 1–50.  
- Villains gradually introduced from Seasons 10–20.  
- Ultimate battles against Nihilum Sovereign occur in Seasons 25–50.  
- Episodes per season: ~30, each with 3–5 chapters.  
- Chapters represent manga-style breakdowns for action, dialogue, and world-building.  
- Armies interact dynamically with battlefield; powers scale with story progression.  
